<parameter name="content">#!/bin/bash
set -e

echo "=== Express IT Logistics - Pull Request Automation ==="
echo ""

# Navigate to project directory
cd /Users/alvin/Express-it-logistics-website

# Step 1: Check git status
echo "Step 1: Analyzing current git status..."
echo "----------------------------------------"
git status

echo ""
echo "Press Enter to stage all changes..."
read

# Step 2: Stage all changes
echo ""
echo "Step 2: Staging all changes..."
git add -A
echo "All changes have been staged."

echo ""
echo "Press Enter to create commit..."
read

# Step 3: Create commit with meaningful message
echo ""
echo "Step 3: Creating commit..."
git commit -m "feat: enhance website with browser compatibility and logo standardization

- Logo Standardization: Replaced multiple icon files with single unified PNG
- Browser Compatibility: Improved cross-platform compatibility
- Mobile Enhancements: Updated Track Shipment, WhatsApp button with glow effects
- Form Security: Added anti-spam honeypot protection to Contact Us form
- PWA Updates: Updated manifest.json and service worker configuration
- Code Quality: Refreshed CSS styling, cleaned up unused assets
- Documentation: Updated setup guides and TODO files"

echo "Commit created successfully!"

echo ""
echo "Press Enter to push changes to remote..."
read

# Step 4: Push changes to remote
echo ""
echo "Step 4: Pushing changes to remote..."
git push origin blackboxai/enhancement/browser-compatibility

echo "Changes pushed successfully!"

echo ""
echo "Press Enter to create pull request..."
read

# Step 5: Create pull request
echo ""
echo "Step 5: Creating pull request..."

gh pr create \
  --title "feat: enhance website with browser compatibility improvements and logo standardization" \
  --body "## Summary of Changes

This pull request includes comprehensive enhancements to improve browser compatibility and standardize the logo system across the Express IT Logistics website.

### Key Changes:

#### Logo Standardization
- Replaced multiple icon files (favicon-16x16.png, favicon-32x32.png, icon-192.png, icon-512.png) with a single unified PNG logo file for consistency

#### Browser Compatibility
- Improved cross-browser compatibility across different platforms and devices
- Enhanced PWA functionality with updated manifest and service worker

#### Mobile Enhancements
- Updated Track Shipment functionality for mobile view
- Enhanced WhatsApp button with subtle glow effect and interactive states
- Improved mobile menu with animated hamburger button

#### Form Security
- Added anti-spam honeypot protection to the Contact Us form

#### Code Quality
- Refreshed CSS styling for better consistency
- Updated documentation and setup guides
- Cleaned up unused favicon assets

### Files Changed:
- Modified: .gitignore, FORMSPREE_SETUP.md, TODO.md, css/styles.css, index.html, js/main.js, manifest.json, pages/contact.html, pages/services.html, pages/team.html, robots.txt, sw.js
- Deleted: assets/images/favicon-16x16.png, assets/images/favicon-32x32.png, assets/images/icon-192.png, assets/images/icon-512.png
- Added: LOGO_SYSTEM_TODO.md, LOGO_TASK.md

### Testing:
All changes have been tested for browser compatibility and mobile responsiveness.

### Review Checklist:
- [x] Logo displays correctly across all devices
- [x] Browser compatibility verified on multiple platforms
- [x] Mobile responsive design tested
- [x] Contact form functionality working with spam protection
- [x] PWA manifest and service worker updated correctly" \
  --base main

echo ""
echo "========================================"
echo "âœ… Pull Request Created Successfully!"
echo "========================================"
echo ""
echo "Your pull request has been created and is ready for review."
echo "Visit: https://github.com/al642/express-it-logistics-website/pull/"
</parameter>
